<div class="pl-md-4">
<div class="font-weight-bold"><a class="text-vdbpurple" href="https://www.vdb-loi.com/kh_publications/transfer-pricing-important-new-developments/">Transfer Pricing – Important New Developments!</a></div>
<div class="text-vdbgray small">June 22, 2018</div>
<div><a class="font-italic text-vdbaqua small" href="https://www.vdb-loi.com/kh_publications/transfer-pricing-important-new-developments/">https://www.vdb-loi.com/kh_publications/transfer-pricing-important-new-developments/</a></div>
<div class="font-italic"><p>VDB Loi have recently had the opportunity to meet senior members of the GDT’s Transfer Pricing team to discuss and clarify certain issues that are not clearly addressed in the new Transfer Pricing (“TP”) regulations. These issues, and the GDT’s current thinking on them, are as follows: Will it be possible to obtain the GDT’s [&hellip;]</p>
